  "title": "Sales Director",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Drive revenue growth and lead strategic sales initiatives for a catering restaurant specializing in Bangladeshi cuisine. Develop and execute sales plans, manage budgets, and build strong client relationships across sectors such as construction.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead the sales team to achieve strategic revenue growth targets aligned with organizational goals</li><li>Develop and implement comprehensive sales plans to expand market presence and client base</li><li>Manage sales budgets effectively to optimize resource allocation and maximize profitability</li><li>Foster and maintain strong client relationships by engaging with stakeholders across sectors including construction</li><li>Apply knowledge of Bangladeshi dishes to tailor marketing strategies that resonate with target clients and enhance customer engagement</li></ul>",
